    "One notable strength of this work is its capability to handle longitudinal datasets, accommodating scenarios where subjects have varying numbers of scans captured at various time intervals.",
    "However, predicting the conversion from ND to MCI poses inherent challenges.",
    "This is primarily because of its difficulty in differentiating between cognitive decline correlated with symptoms of MCI and cognitive decline while maintaining a stable baseline cognitive function.",
